            {
                "comment": "Very professional class. Dr. Mulvihill really cares that you become a better writer. Class was more writing heavy than reading, which I really liked. We had 1 on 1 meetings to go over drafts of every writing assignment which was awesome. Take the class seriously and you'll do well and learn a lot",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "I took this class to satisfy a Comm A requirement. John was an amazing professor. Some of the homework he assigned seemed like busy work, but it was overall a great class. He was very informative, respectful, and helpful. Outside of class, he could be easily accessed. It's disappointing that I won't be able to take another class with him. ",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Professor Mulvihill was one of the best professors I have had. He was very easy to get in contact with and responded within an hour. He was always willing to Zoom if you needed clarification or help on an assignment. He also would read each students' paper and meet with them to give feedback and advice. He was a very nice guy! 100% recommend!!",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
